# ── SafePulse Frontend Environment ───────────────────────────────────────────
# In Codespaces with the Vite proxy enabled (vite.config.ts → proxy),
# you can leave this as /api and requests will be proxied to port 8000.
#
# When deploying to AWS Amplify (production), set this to your full EC2 URL:
#   VITE_API_BASE_URL=https://api.yourdomain.com
VITE_API_BASE_URL=/api
